I must leave it.

42
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,860
I must leave it now.

43
00:04:16,605 --> 00:04:19,505
But how to escape one's city?

44
00:04:19,775 --> 00:04:24,407
How to wake oneself enough
for the frightening task...

45
00:04:24,447 --> 00:04:27,347
of how to find one's way out?

46
00:04:30,286 --> 00:04:33,874
The greatest urban train yard
in the world.

47
00:04:33,914 --> 00:04:36,014
Arteries. Iron veins.

48
00:04:36,917 --> 00:04:38,917
Ways out.

49
