The dream train.

50
00:04:41,297 --> 00:04:43,297
Chugging, dreaming.

51
00:04:45,968 --> 00:04:50,168
Sleep-chugging,
out of the lap of the city.

52
00:04:52,016 --> 00:04:55,354
Out of the lap described
by the Forks,

53
00:04:55,394 --> 00:04:58,194
of the Red, the Assiniboine.

54
00:04:59,148 --> 00:05:01,148
The Forks,

55
00:05:01,984 --> 00:05:04,384
Assiniboine and the Red.

56
00:05:05,362 --> 00:05:13,455
The rivers that forced animals and hunters
alike onto the same waterside pathways.

57
